<br>
(1) Portal fragments should be done away with. Same for any spell that requires a component, really. In my opinion, components should be used to make potions, via alchemy. <br>
<br>
(2) Druids should not get Nexus Portal, but should get a port to someplace relatively close, like Dawnshroud (I think some druid rings in Dawnshroud would be appropriate)<br>
<br>
A port should work from anywhere. Shouldn't matter if it's druid, or wizard. <br>
